title: Zimbabwe Won’t Seek Extradition of American Who Killed Cecil the Lion
text:
HARARE, Zimbabwe—Zimbabwe is no longer pressing for the extradition of Walter Palmer, the American dentist who killed a well-known lion called Cecil, a cabinet minister said Monday.
Dr. Palmer can now safely return to Zimbabwe as a tourist because he hadn’t broken the country’s hunting laws, Environment, Water and Climate Minister Oppah Muchinguri-Kashiri told reporters.
